channel.description:
WT-Fakawi's original thread is [url=http://82.92.130.193/forums/showthread.php?p=27908#post27908]here[/url][QUOTE=WT-Fakawi][CENTER][SIZE="6"][COLOR="Red"][B]Long Live Runescape![/B][/COLOR][/SIZE]
[SIZE="4"]Let's celebrate our beloved game with a big goofy show...![/SIZE]
[COLOR="Red"][SIZE="7"][B]Comedytrain![/B][/SIZE][/COLOR][/CENTER]
[SIZE="4"][CENTER][COLOR="Red"][B]July 14th 23:00 GMT/18:00 EST [COLOR="Black"]World-1[/COLOR] Falador Square.[/B][/COLOR][/CENTER][/SIZE]
[SIZE="4"] The rules are very simple: [LIST] [*]1.We all dress up in the same goofy outfit. (dress code explained below...) [*]2.We [B]follow [/B]each other around the free world goofing legit players, and then... [*]3.We walk to the wildy where we kill each other bear-handed. [SIZE="1"][*]4.[B] NO TALK ABOUT CHEATING! No disrespect. No BOTS/AUTOTALKERS/SRL, please[/B] Lets make this a fun thing![/SIZE][/LIST][/SIZE]
[B][SIZE="4"] We assemble around [/SIZE][/B]
- [COLOR="Red"]22:00 GMT[/COLOR] /[COLOR="Red"]17:00 EST[/COLOR] at [B]World-1[/B] Falador Square. - We take off ([B]follow[/B]) at [COLOR="Red"]23:00[/COLOR], go to the Falador park and gesture/annoy/play with the aristocrats. [B][COLOR="Red"]Follow each other as much as possible.[/COLOR][/B] Shouldnt be a problem hopefully.... - At [COLOR="Red"]23:20[/COLOR] we assemble again at Bot Spot #1 commemorating the intelligence of the Chinese. - At [COLOR="Red"]23:20[/COLOR] we take of ([B]follow[/B]) for a yourney to Draynor where we will goof around for another[COLOR="Red"] 20[/COLOR] minutes. - At[COLOR="Red"] 23:40[/COLOR] we reassemble at Lumbridge and walk ([B]follow[/B]) all the way up Varrock. - At [COLOR="Red"]00:00[/COLOR] we reassemble at the border of the wild above Varrock. At exactly [COLOR="Red"]00:00 on my mark[/COLOR], we run to the wild and start killing each other bear-handed. No weapons allowed! He who stands last, erm.... stands last. The rest will say goodbye in Lumbridge :D
[B][CENTER]DRESS CODE:[/CENTER][/B] [CENTER]
[IMG]http://www.villavu.com/Pictures/dresscode.jpg[/img][/CENTER]
[B][CENTER][SIZE="5"]
How to makeover to comedytrain dresscode:[/SIZE][/CENTER][/B]
[B][LIST] [*]1. Have 7k in your inventory. [*]2. Goto MakeOver Mage and make Male/blond [*]3. Goto HairDresser and give yourselfs a nice Blue Monk Cut! and a long Blue Beard. Goofy enough? [*]4. Goto Clothes Shop in Varrock and makeover default torso/legs in Blue [*]5. Done. [/LIST][/B]
[IMG]http://www.villavu.com/Pictures/comedytrain1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://www.villavu.com/Pictures/comedytrain2.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://www.villavu.com/Pictures/comedytrain3.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://www.villavu.com/Pictures/comedytrain4.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://www.villavu.com/Pictures/comedytrain5.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://www.villavu.com/Pictures/comedytrainmain.jpg[/img]
[B][SIZE="5"][CENTER] This is the route we will walk...[/CENTER][/SIZE][/B]
[IMG]http://www.villavu.com/Pictures/comedytrain8.jpg[/img]
[SIZE="4"][CENTER][COLOR="Red"][B]July 14th 23:00 GMT/18:00 EST [COLOR="Black"]World-1[/COLOR] Falador Square.[/B][/COLOR][/CENTER][/SIZE]
Once again: please no talks on cheating etc. That is not the intention of a comedytrain. We do this for fun, to entertain, to show off, radiate positive energy, not to insult and bring down.
[CENTER] [B][SIZE="7"][COLOR="Red"] DONT MISS IT![/COLOR][/SIZE][/B][/CENTER]
[SIZE="4"][CENTER][COLOR="Red"][B]July 14th 23:00 GMT/18:00 EST [COLOR="Black"]World-1[/COLOR] Falador Square.[/B][/COLOR][/CENTER][/SIZE]
